Add scrollbar for changing the distance dinamically.
issue.body:
All the client and server code to transmit and process the distance update is already there. The only thing that lacks is having the scrollbar in the layout and emiting a message to the messagebus, like here with the radius field in the login screen:

https://github.com/radhikabhatt/locationbasedChat/blob/master/app/public/js/views/main.js#L44

```
this.vent.trigger("radiusUpdate", value);
```
